(Here's your vollenteer)

Spears::

She got up and looked at Firearm. "I need some air."
She walked out of the meeting room and walked out towards the base 
entrance.  She walked a few yards away from the ship.  She was 
missing Striker terribly.  She sighed and looked around.  She was 
getting tired of living. She was finding it harder to live without 
him. She took a few deep breathed and tried to keep calm. But that 
was getting harder and harder to do.

> ::Ramus::
> 
>     The Stasis pod opened, out climbed a near complete copy of 
Ramulus. The only real difference was the color, and the Spark. He 
started off toward his brothers signal, at the CF.
